init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States is now the only superpower in the world, and the only country that has access to nuclear weapons.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's also the only country that has the ability to travel to space.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is now a powder keg, and the U.S. is the only one with a match.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States has three choices:

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It can stay in exile, it can try to re-establish contact with the other nations, or it can try to conquer the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States chooses to conquer the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States has a small army, but it has the most advanced weapons in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States has a plan.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The plan is to send a team of soldiers to every country in the world, and to take over the country without firing a shot.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can choose to rule the world with an iron fist, or you can choose to be a benevolent ruler.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The US was the most powerful nation on Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The US had the ability to terraform planets and make them habitable for humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I dont know, but i wouldnt count out the possibility.
